\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](......Hm? Is it just my imagination? It feels like someone
is watching me... No, maybe I'm just being
paranoid...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Ever since my debut, I've become a bit sensitive to
people's gazes... Maybe it's just my
imagination...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](There's a spreading darkness that feels like it's sucking
me in...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](There's a spreading darkness that feels like it's sucking
me in...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](......Hm? Just now, amidst the sound of the wind, I faintly
heard what seemed like a woman's voice...)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]No way... such an old Western-style mansion...

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](----...N-No, it must be my imagination! I have absolutely no
psychic abilities, so it's definitely just my
imagination!)
